About Us























Brookside Mezzanine Partners takes a long-term, partnership-based approach to mezzanine investments.





About Us




With over $500 million under management, Brookside Mezzanine Partners invests subordinated debt and minority equity in small and mid-sized companies throughout the United States. We invest up to $20 million per transaction and have the resources to complete larger transactions as well in conjunction with our limited partners and associates. While our investments are diversified by both industry and geography, Brookside Mezzanine Partners has over a decade of experience within the manufacturing, business services, distribution, restaurant/retail and healthcare sectors. We invest in both sponsored and non-sponsored transactions and provide junior capital and unitranche financing to support buyouts, leveraged recapitalizations, strategic acquisitions, dividends and growth capital.

Brookside Mezzanine Partners takes a long-term, partnership-based approach to its mezzanine investments. The Firm has extensive experience working with management teams, intermediaries, as well as private equity sponsors to structure transactions that makes sense for each unique situation. We have experience providing capital to various industries across a variety of economic and capital market conditions.


































 




















